scene.message:
Student: Outside is in such an{nl}
uproar, yet here it's quiet...{waitkey}Why don't any demons appear{nl}
here, I wonder? Could it be{nl}
divine protection?{waitkey}{ret}

The Hiremon Stone{nl}
A massive boulder unearthed{nl}
in 1963 when the school was{nl}
first built.{waitkey}{clearbox}Its rock is samataite, yet{nl}
magnetic anomalies have been{nl}
detected within it.{waitkey}{clearbox}Legend holds that a celestial{nl}
being named Hiremon{waitkey}cast it down from the heavens{nl}
as a guardian stone for{nl}
Mikage Town.{waitkey}{ret}
